06:06.600 --> 06:07.735
* HERE WE GO
* HERE WE GO

06:07.768 --> 06:09.069
* ON THE ROAD
* ON THE ROAD

06:09.102 --> 06:10.337
* PLENTY SUN
* PLENTY SUN

06:10.370 --> 06:11.405
* FIRED UP
* FIRED UP

06:11.439 --> 06:12.706
* FIRED UP
* FIRED UP

06:12.740 --> 06:14.408
* FIRED UP
